#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.28"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.28:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.28:0.2"
msgid "3. Pañcaṅgikavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: pañcaṅgikasamādhisuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.28:0.3"
msgid "28. Pañcaṅgikasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.25"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:1.1"
msgid "“Ariyassa, bhikkhave, pañcaṅgikassa sammāsamādhissa bhāvanaṃ desessāmi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:1.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:1.4"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:2.1"
msgid "“Katamā ca, bhikkhave, ariyassa pañcaṅgikassa sammāsamādhissa bhāvanā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja "
"viharati."
msgstr ""

# From the passage on charnel ground contemplations (MN 10, etc) we can see that imameva kaya specifically means “one’s own body” as opposed to the bodies of others.
msgctxt "an5.28:2.3"
msgid ""
"So imameva kāyaṃ vivekajena pītisukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti "
"parippharati; nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa vivekajena pītisukhena apphuṭaṃ "
"hoti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: nhāpako → nahāpako (bj, pts1)
#. VAR: nhānīyacuṇṇāni → nahāniyacuṇṇāni (bj, pts1) | nhāniyacuṇṇāni (s1-3)
#. VAR: Sāyaṃ → saṃsā (si) | sā’ssa (pts1)
#. VAR: nhānīyapiṇḍi → nahāniyapiṇḍi (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
#. VAR: paggharinī → paggharati (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.28:2.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, dakkho nhāpako vā nhāpakantevāsī vā kaṃsathāle "
"nhānīyacuṇṇāni ākiritvā udakena paripphosakaṃ paripphosakaṃ sanneyya. Sāyaṃ "
"nhānīyapiṇḍi snehānugatā snehaparetā santarabāhirā phuṭā snehena, na ca "
"paggharinī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:2.5"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu imameva kāyaṃ vivekajena pītisukhena "
"abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:2.6"
msgid "nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa vivekajena pītisukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:2.7"
msgid ""
"Ariyassa, bhikkhave, pañcaṅgikassa sammāsamādhissa ayaṃ paṭhamā bhāvanā. (1)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.26"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā … pe … dutiyaṃ "
"jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:3.2"
msgid ""
"So imameva kāyaṃ samādhijena pītisukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti "
"parippharati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:3.3"
msgid "nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa samādhijena pītisukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: ubbhidodako → ubbhitodako (s1-3, km, mr)
#. VAR: dhāraṃ nānuppaveccheyya → devo ca na kālena … anuppaveccheyya (pts1)
msgctxt "an5.28:3.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, udakarahado gambhīro ubbhidodako. Tassa nevassa "
"puratthimāya disāya udakassa āyamukhaṃ, na pacchimāya disāya udakassa "
"āyamukhaṃ, na uttarāya disāya udakassa āyamukhaṃ, na dakkhiṇāya disāya "
"udakassa āyamukhaṃ, devo ca kālena kālaṃ sammā dhāraṃ nānuppaveccheyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:3.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho tamhāva udakarahadā sītā vāridhārā ubbhijjitvā tameva udakarahadaṃ "
"sītena vārinā abhisandeyya parisandeyya paripūreyya paripphareyya; nāssa "
"kiñci sabbāvato udakarahadassa sītena vārinā apphuṭaṃ assa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:3.6"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu imameva kāyaṃ samādhijena pītisukhena "
"abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:3.7"
msgid "nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa samādhijena pītisukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:3.8"
msgid ""
"Ariyassa, bhikkhave, pañcaṅgikassa sammāsamādhissa ayaṃ dutiyā bhāvanā. (2)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pītiyā ca virāgā … pe … tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ "
"upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:4.2"
msgid ""
"So imameva kāyaṃ nippītikena sukhena abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti "
"parippharati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:4.3"
msgid "nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa nippītikena sukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:4.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, uppaliniyaṃ vā paduminiyaṃ vā puṇḍarīkiniyaṃ vā "
"appekaccāni uppalāni vā padumāni vā puṇḍarīkāni vā udake jātāni udake "
"saṃvaḍḍhāni udakānuggatāni anto nimuggaposīni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:4.5"
msgid ""
"Tāni yāva caggā yāva ca mūlā sītena vārinā abhisannāni parisannāni "
"paripūrāni paripphuṭāni;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:4.6"
msgid ""
"nāssa kiñci sabbāvataṃ uppalānaṃ vā padumānaṃ vā puṇḍarīkānaṃ vā sītena "
"vārinā apphuṭaṃ assa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:4.7"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu imameva kāyaṃ nippītikena sukhena "
"abhisandeti parisandeti paripūreti parippharati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:4.8"
msgid "nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa nippītikena sukhena apphuṭaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:4.9"
msgid ""
"Ariyassa, bhikkhave, pañcaṅgikassa sammāsamādhissa ayaṃ tatiyā bhāvanā. (3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.27"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sukhassa ca pahānā … pe … catutthaṃ jhānaṃ "
"upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:5.2"
msgid ""
"So imameva kāyaṃ parisuddhena cetasā pariyodātena pharitvā nisinno hoti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:5.3"
msgid ""
"nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa parisuddhena cetasā pariyodātena apphuṭaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:5.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso odātena vatthena sasīsaṃ pārupitvā nisinno "
"assa;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:5.5"
msgid "nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa odātena vatthena apphuṭaṃ assa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:5.6"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu imameva kāyaṃ parisuddhena cetasā "
"pariyodātena pharitvā nisinno hoti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:5.7"
msgid ""
"nāssa kiñci sabbāvato kāyassa parisuddhena cetasā pariyodātena apphuṭaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:5.8"
msgid ""
"Ariyassa, bhikkhave, pañcaṅgikassa sammāsamādhissa ayaṃ catutthā bhāvanā. (4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:6.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno paccavekkhaṇānimittaṃ suggahitaṃ hoti "
"sumanasikataṃ sūpadhāritaṃ suppaṭividdhaṃ paññāya."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: aññova aññaṃ → añño vā aññaṃ (bj, s1-3, km) | añño vā aññaṃ vā (si) | añño aññaṃ (?)
msgctxt "an5.28:6.2"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, aññova aññaṃ paccavekkheyya, ṭhito vā nisinnaṃ "
"paccavekkheyya, nisinno vā nipannaṃ paccavekkheyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:6.3"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno paccavekkhaṇānimittaṃ suggahitaṃ hoti "
"sumanasikataṃ sūpadhāritaṃ suppaṭividdhaṃ paññāya."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: pañcamā → pañcamī (bj)
msgctxt "an5.28:6.4"
msgid ""
"Ariyassa, bhikkhave, pañcaṅgikassa sammāsamādhissa ayaṃ pañcamā bhāvanā. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
#. VAR: kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu → evaṃ bhāvite kho bhikkhave (s1-3)
msgctxt "an5.28:7.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvite kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariye pañcaṅgike sammāsamādhimhi evaṃ "
"bahulīkate yassa yassa abhiññāsacchikaraṇīyassa dhammassa cittaṃ "
"abhininnāmeti abhiññāsacchikiriyāya, tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti "
"sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.28"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:8.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, udakamaṇiko ādhāre ṭhapito pūro udakassa samatittiko "
"kākapeyyo."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: āvajjeyya → āvaṭṭeyya (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an5.28:8.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ balavā puriso yato yato āvajjeyya, āgaccheyya udakan”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:8.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:8.4"
msgid ""
"“Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ bhāvite ariye pañcaṅgike "
"sammāsamādhimhi evaṃ bahulīkate yassa yassa abhiññāsacchikaraṇīyassa "
"dhammassa cittaṃ abhininnāmeti abhiññāsacchikiriyāya, tatra tatreva "
"sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:9.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, same bhūmibhāge pokkharaṇī caturaṃsā ālibaddhā pūrā "
"udakassa samatittikā kākapeyyā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:9.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ balavā puriso yato yato āliṃ muñceyya, āgaccheyya udakan”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:9.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:9.4"
msgid ""
"“Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ bhāvite ariye pañcaṅgike "
"sammāsamādhimhi evaṃ bahulīkate yassa yassa abhiññāsacchikaraṇīyassa "
"dhammassa … pe … sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
#. VAR: catumahāpathe → cātummahāpathe (bj, pts1) | catummahāpathe (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an5.28:10.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, subhūmiyaṃ catumahāpathe ājaññaratho yutto assa ṭhito "
"odhastapatodo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:10.2"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ dakkho yoggācariyo assadammasārathi abhiruhitvā vāmena hatthena "
"rasmiyo gahetvā dakkhiṇena hatthena patodaṃ gahetvā yenicchakaṃ yadicchakaṃ "
"sāreyyapi paccāsāreyyapi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:10.3"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ bhāvite ariye pañcaṅgike "
"sammāsamādhimhi evaṃ bahulīkate yassa yassa abhiññāsacchikaraṇīyassa "
"dhammassa cittaṃ abhininnāmeti abhiññāsacchikiriyāya, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:10.4"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.29"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:11.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhaveyyaṃ—ekopi hutvā "
"bahudhā assaṃ … pe … yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:11.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:12.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘dibbāya sotadhātuyā visuddhāya atikkantamānusikāya ubho "
"sadde suṇeyyaṃ—dibbe ca mānuse ca ye dūre santike cā’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:12.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:13.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ cetasā ceto paricca "
"pajāneyyaṃ—sarāgaṃ vā cittaṃ sarāgaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, vītarāgaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ vītarāgaṃ cittanti pajāneyyaṃ, sadosaṃ vā cittaṃ … vītadosaṃ vā "
"cittaṃ … samohaṃ vā cittaṃ … vītamohaṃ vā cittaṃ … saṅkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ … "
"vikkhittaṃ vā cittaṃ … mahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ … amahaggataṃ vā cittaṃ … "
"sauttaraṃ vā cittaṃ … anuttaraṃ vā cittaṃ … samāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ … asamāhitaṃ "
"vā cittaṃ … vimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ … avimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ avimuttaṃ cittanti "
"pajāneyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:13.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:14.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—"
"ekampi jātiṃ, dvepi jātiyo … pe … iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ "
"pubbenivāsaṃ anussareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:14.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:15.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena … pe … "
"yathākammūpage satte pajāneyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:15.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "an5.28:16.1"
msgid ""
"So sace ākaṅkhati: ‘āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ "
"diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.28:16.2"
msgid "tatra tatreva sakkhibhabbataṃ pāpuṇāti sati sati āyatane”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.28:16.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
